narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Professor Wichowsky has a position at another school next year so won't be teaching this. If she does return to teach, take this course! It's a great seminar on a very interesting (and often not marginalized) topic.

This is a pretty good class, except the readings were really long and extremely boring. It was tough to do all the readings, but I'd suggest picking the shortest one and reading that so you can talk about it.
I would say take this class, but Prof Wichowsky is leaving and she was the best part of the class...
